nodes.text: Vyndal was a planet located in the galaxy that was covered with colorful forests, and rocky plains. Vyndal was also the homeworld to a unknown race.

At some point, a Jedi piloting a Eta 2 Actis-class light interceptor crashed on Vyndal and was killed. Later around 4 BBY, a human male named Yeleb took the Jedi's lightsaber, and took it as his own weapon. During 4 BBY, a skirmish took place between the natives, Yaleb, Kanan Jarrus, and The Grand Inquisitor.
